Rare Special Items.title: Bayonet | Fade
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted by airbrushing transparent paints that fade together over a chrome base coat.
Rare Special Items.lore: This isn't just a weapon, it's a conversation piece - Imogen, Arms Dealer In Training

Rare Special Items.title: Bayonet | Slaughter
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted in a zebra-stripe pattern with aluminum and chrome paints with various reflectivities, and has then been covered with a tomato red candy coat.

Rare Special Items.lore: A little color never hurt anyone

Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted using a tangle of masking tape as a stencil.

Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted using mesh fencing and cardboard cutouts as stencils.

Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a sci-fi design.
Covert Skins.lore: Anyone can predict the future... a visionary shapes it

Covert Skins.title: Sawed-Off | The Kraken
Covert Skins.desc: It has been hand painted with an image of an octopus.

Classified Skins.title: AWP | Redline
Classified Skins.desc: It has been painted using a carbon fiber hydrographic and a dry-transfer decal of a red pinstripe.
Classified Skins.lore: Never be afraid to push it to the limit

Classified Skins.title: M4A1-S | Guardian
Classified Skins.desc: It has been painted cobalt blue and stenciled with the CT logo on the magazine.
Classified Skins.lore: I don't have to like you, I have to keep you safe - Carmen Cocinero, Extraction Expert

Classified Skins.title: P250 | Mehndi
Classified Skins.desc: It has been painted with a hydrographic in a paisley pattern.

Restricted Skins.title: MP9 | Rose Iron
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been hand painted with a rose and thorn motif in metallic paints of different colors.

Restricted Skins.title: Dual Berettas | Marina
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been painted with a hydrographic in a contrasting yellow and blue pattern.
Restricted Skins.lore: Some people will call you a hero... others a villain

Restricted Skins.title: FAMAS | Pulse
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been painted with a hydrographic of bold fuchsia fragments.
Restricted Skins.lore: Striking colors for a striking weapon

Restricted Skins.title: Nova | Rising Skull
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been customized with an image of a skull using matte paints and an oil-based paint marker.
Restricted Skins.lore: Mr. Izaki, I'm not complaining... but how many shotguns do you need? - Imogen and The Oni, Part 1

Mil-Spec Skins.title: Galil AR | Sandstorm
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted using a hydrographic in a purple and beige graphic design.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: It'll take more than a tarp to protect you

Mil-Spec Skins.title: PP-Bizon | Cobalt Halftone
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted using a hydrographic in an oversized halftone pattern over a base coat of turquoise metallic paint.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Felix, you and I both know Valeria's about to wage a war. The only question is are you prepared? - Booth, Arms Dealer

Mil-Spec Skins.title: Five-SeveN | Kami
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted using a hydrographic in a Japanese manga pattern.

Mil-Spec Skins.title: M249 | Magma
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has copper plated parts that have been masked in a magma pattern and given a red patina using sodium chloride and high heat. Unmasked areas have subsequently been darkened via oxidization using liver of sulfur.
